#' hybridForecast: Hybrid Time Series Forecasting with Trend, Seasonality, and Machine Learning
#'
#' This package provides a hybrid modeling framework for time series forecasting, combining trend and seasonal decomposition with machine learning models like XGBoost, LightGBM, and neural networks.
#'
#' @docType package
#' @name hybridForecast
#'
